This app was tested on the emulator Pixel 4A, API 30, release name: "R"
To prevent issues with Firebase, please use Emulator version 31.2.9.
To check emulator version, go to SDK Manager > Android SDk > SDK Tools
Please note that Emulator version 31.3.10 has had a bug with Firebase and will not work.
Feel free to refer to this video for ease of reference in downgrading to 31.2.9:
"https://youtu.be/qo3SbdbXFos"